COALESCE(CASE WHEN SUM(rx.L1BitCount) * L2Factor > 0.0005 * SUM(rx.LastArrivalTime - rx.FirstArrivalTime) THEN ((SUM(rx.L1BitCount) * L2Factor / SUM(rx.LastArrivalTime - rx.FirstArrivalTime))) END, 0) AS IrMean,
COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount), SUM(TxFrameCount)) AS FlCount,
(1e2 * COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount)/ SUM(TxFrameCount), 1)) AS Flr,
SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(rx.FrameCount), 0) AS RxFrameCount,
SUM(rx.TotalLatency) AS FtdTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinLatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalLatency)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FtdMean,
COALESCE(MAX(rx.Maxlatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMax,
SUM(rx.TotalJitter) AS FdvTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinJitter) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FdvMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalJitter)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FdvMean,

sql_statement.static: SELECT ServiceId, TxOk,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.L1BitCount) * L2Factor / SUM(rx.LastArrivalTime - rx.FirstArrivalTime), 0) AS IrMean,
COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount), SUM(TxFrameCount)) AS FlCount,
(1e2 * COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount)/ SUM(TxFrameCount), 1)) AS Flr,
SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(rx.FrameCount), 0) AS RxFrameCount,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.LateFrameCount), 0) AS LateCount, COALESCE(SUM(rx.OutSeqFrameCount), 0) AS OosCount,
SUM(rx.TotalLatency) AS FtdTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinLatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalLatency)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FtdMean,
COALESCE(MAX(rx.Maxlatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMax,
SUM(rx.TotalJitter) AS FdvTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinJitter) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FdvMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalJitter)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FdvMean,
COALESCE(MAX(rx.MaxJitter) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FdvMax
FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, Sb.L2Rate/Sb.BpsLoad AS L2Factor, Sb.Handle AS SbHandle,
COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount>0,0) AS TxOk, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount,
CAST(SUBSTR(Tag.Name,4) AS INTEGER) AS ServiceId, Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd
FROM StreamBlock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock
JOIN RelationTable AS rt ON Sb.Handle=rt.SourceHnd JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort)
WHERE SbActive GROUP BY ServiceId
SELECT ServiceId, ServiceName, TxOk, Cf.CIR*(1-Cf.FLR/100.0)<=Int.IrMean AS RateOk,
Int.Flr<=Cf.FLR AS FlrOk, (Int.FtdMax IS NOT NULL AND Int.FtdMax<=cf.FTD) AS FtdOk,
(Int.FdvMax IS NOT NULL AND Int.FdvMax<=cf.FDV) AS FdvOk, Cf.CIR AS SvcCir, IrMean,
Cf.CIR*(1-Cf.FLR/100.0) AS IrThreshold, TxFrameCount, RxFrameCount, LateCount, OosCount, FlCount, Int.Flr, Cf.FLR AS SvcFlr,
FtdMin, FtdMean, FtdMax, Cf.FTD AS SvcFtd, FdvMin, FdvMean, FdvMax, Cf.FDV AS SvcFdv
FROM y1564Config AS Cf JOIN y1564PerfIntRes AS Int ON Cf.rowid=Int.ServiceId
